WEBVTT

00:00.480 --> 00:01.440
Spare him

00:01.800 --> 00:04.160
All the court officials are waiting for a result

00:04.600 --> 00:05.360
Spare him

00:05.440 --> 00:07.080
Who will take the blame for treason?

00:08.680 --> 00:09.640
You?

00:09.960 --> 00:11.240
Or your elder brother?

00:11.640 --> 00:13.280
Or will you investigate further

00:13.640 --> 00:15.400
And break with the Chen family?

00:18.480 --> 00:19.400
Do you think

00:19.600 --> 00:21.800
Only you can see the situation clearly?

00:21.880 --> 00:23.400
Can't I see it clearly?

00:30.840 --> 00:31.640
Father

00:48.480 --> 00:50.080
Our Sikong family

00:50.280 --> 00:51.640
After the great chaos

00:52.200 --> 00:53.840
Could still establish itself in the south

00:54.400 --> 00:56.240
Relied on two great families

00:57.240 --> 00:59.000
The Zu family leading troops abroad

00:59.400 --> 01:01.200
The Chen family governing court affairs

01:01.280 --> 01:02.120
These two families

01:03.160 --> 01:05.080
If either corner collapses

01:05.440 --> 01:07.120
The entire structure will fall

01:10.880 --> 01:11.760
Now

01:12.000 --> 01:13.200
We're not yet firmly established

01:13.280 --> 01:15.240
It's not yet time to move against them

01:16.640 --> 01:17.280
So

01:17.760 --> 01:18.640
The troops were

01:18.640 --> 01:19.640
Deployed by Chu Huan

01:19.800 --> 01:20.720
The weapons and armor

01:20.720 --> 01:22.560
Were also planted by Chu Huan to frame you

01:23.240 --> 01:23.760
This is

01:23.760 --> 01:25.280
The only way to save you

01:25.280 --> 01:26.720
Do you understand?

01:29.200 --> 01:30.400
I've told you so much

01:30.400 --> 01:31.280
Do you understand?

01:31.320 --> 01:32.000
Answer
